bodyText: Finnish Series of Beer Pong is organized once again and for the firs time in the city of Turku!
More info regarding the event and ticket sales will be avalible momenteraily
The tournament is arranged in co-operation by Aalto Beer Pong, Beer Pong Turku and Lappeenranta Beer Pong. Tournament is played on WSOBP rules. Please see the rules in advance here.
